trans-unit.source: The ActiveDirectorySchedule class represents the weekly schedule for an Active Directory Domain Services replication.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ActiveDirectorySchedule representerer ukentlig tidsplan for en Active Directory Domain Services-replikeringen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule"></xref> class, using the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule"> </xref> class, ved hjelp av den angitte <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule"></xref> object that is copied to this object.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule"> </xref> objektet som blir kopiert til dette objektet.

trans-unit.source: schedule is .
trans-unit.target: scheduleis .

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a three-dimensional array that indicates at what time during the week that the source is available for replication.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en tredimensjonale matrise som angir når under uken at kilden er tilgjengelig for replikering.

trans-unit.source: A three-dimensional array of <xref:System.Boolean> elements in which the element is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the source is available for replication during that specific 15-minute interval.
trans-unit.target: En tredimensjonale rekke <xref:System.Boolean>elementer som elementet er <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> hvis kilden er tilgjengelig for replikering under dette bestemte 15 minutter-intervallet.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: The element is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the source is not available for replication.
trans-unit.target: Elementet er <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> hvis kilden ikke er tilgjengelig for replikering.

trans-unit.source: The array is in the form RawSchedule[<day-of-week>, <hour>, <15-minute interval>].
trans-unit.target: Matrisen er formatet RawSchedule [<dag i uken>, <time>, <15 minutter intervallet>].

trans-unit.source: All of these values are zero-based and the week begins at 00:00 on Sunday morning, Coordinated Universal Time.
trans-unit.target: Alle disse verdiene er nullbasert og uken begynner på søndag morgen, Coordinated Universal Time 00:00.

trans-unit.source: The following are the valid values for the day-of-week.
trans-unit.target: Følgende er gyldige verdier for i dag-av-uken.

trans-unit.source: Day-of-week value
trans-unit.target: Verdien som dagen i uken

trans-unit.source: Indicated day of the week.
trans-unit.target: Angitte ukedagen.

trans-unit.source: Sunday
trans-unit.target: Søndag

trans-unit.source: Monday
trans-unit.target: Mandag

trans-unit.source: Tuesday
trans-unit.target: Tirsdag

trans-unit.source: Wednesday
trans-unit.target: Onsdag

trans-unit.source: Thursday
trans-unit.target: Torsdag

trans-unit.source: Friday
trans-unit.target: Fredag

trans-unit.source: Saturday
trans-unit.target: Lørdag

trans-unit.source: The hour is zero-based and specified in 24-hour format.
trans-unit.target: Timen er nullbasert og som er angitt i 24-timers format.

trans-unit.source: For example, 2 P.M.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel 14.

trans-unit.source: would be specified as 14.
trans-unit.target: kan angis som 14.

trans-unit.source: Valid values are 0-23.
trans-unit.target: Gyldige verdier er 0-23.

trans-unit.source: The 15-minute interval specifies the 15-minute block within the hour that the source is available for replication.
trans-unit.target: Intervallet 15 minutter angir blokken 15 minutter i timen kilden er tilgjengelig for replikering.

trans-unit.source: The following table identifies the possible values for the 15-minute interval.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser mulige verdier for 15 minutter-intervallet.

trans-unit.source: 15-minute interval
trans-unit.target: intervallet for&15; minutter

trans-unit.source: Description
trans-unit.target: Beskrivelse

trans-unit.source: The source is available for replication from 0 to 14 minutes after the hour.
trans-unit.target: Kilden er tilgjengelig for replikering fra 0 til 14 minutter etter timen.

trans-unit.source: The source is available for replication from 15 to 29 minutes after the hour.
trans-unit.target: Kilden er tilgjengelig for replikering fra 15 til 29 minutter etter timen.

trans-unit.source: The source is available for replication from 30 to 44 minutes after the hour.
trans-unit.target: Kilden er tilgjengelig for replikering fra 30 til 44 minutter etter timen.

trans-unit.source: The source is available for replication from 45 to 59 minutes after the hour.
trans-unit.target: Kilden er tilgjengelig for replikering fra 45 til 59 minutter etter timen.

trans-unit.source: The following C# example shows how to use this property to determine if the source is available for replication at 15:50 Coordinated Universal Time on Tuesday.
trans-unit.target: C# eksemplet viser hvordan du bruker denne egenskapen til å avgjøre om kilden er tilgjengelig for replikering på 15:50 Coordinated Universal Time tirsdag.

trans-unit.source: ```c# Boolean isAvailable = scheduleObject.RawSchedule[2, 15, 3]; ``` The following C# example shows how to use this property to calculate the 15-minute interval at runtime by dividing the minutes by 15.
trans-unit.target: ```c# Boolean isAvailable = scheduleObject.RawSchedule[2, 15, 3]; ```C# eksemplet viser hvordan du bruker denne egenskapen til å beregne 15 minutter intervallet under kjøring ved å dele 15 minutter.

trans-unit.source: Resets the entire schedule to unavailable.
trans-unit.target: Tilbakestiller hele tidsplanen til utilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: Adds a range of times for every day of the week to the schedule.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en rekke ganger for hver dag i uken i tidsplanen.

trans-unit.source: All of the parameters in this method are inclusive.
trans-unit.target: Alle parameterne i denne metoden er inklusive.

trans-unit.source: This method is cumulative and does not remove any existing schedule information.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er kumulativ og fjernes ikke en eksisterende tidsplaninformasjon.

trans-unit.source: If an existing schedule and the new schedule overlap, the result will still be cumulative.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en eksisterende tidsplan, og den nye tidsplanen overlapper, kan resultatet fortsatt kumulativ.

trans-unit.source: To clear the schedule, use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule.ResetSchedule%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil fjerne en tidsplan, kan du bruke den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule.ResetSchedule%2A>metoden.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchedule.ResetSchedule%2A>
